18#include <sys/cdefs.h>
19#ifndef lint
20__RCSID("$NetBSD: print-sip.c,v 1.8 2017/09/08 14:01:13 christos Exp $");
21#endif
22
23/* \summary: Session Initiation Protocol (SIP) printer */
24
25#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
26#include "config.h"
27#endif
28
29#include <netdissect-stdinc.h>
30
31#include "netdissect.h"
32#include "extract.h"
33
34static const char *sipcmds[] = {
35 "ACK",
36 "BYE",
37 "CANCEL",
38 "DO",
39 "INFO",
40 "INVITE",
41 "MESSAGE",
42 "NOTIFY",
43 "OPTIONS",
44 "PRACK",
45 "QAUTH",
46 "REFER",
47 "REGISTER",
48 "SPRACK",
49 "SUBSCRIBE",
50 "UPDATE",
51 "PUBLISH",
52 NULL
53};
54
55void
56sip_print(netdissect_options *ndo, const u_char *pptr, u_int len)
57{
58 txtproto_print(ndo, pptr, len, "sip", sipcmds, RESP_CODE_SECOND_TOKEN);
59}
